# Cursor Adapter

Note: This adapter helps us "talk" to Cursor (https://cursor.com/) in a way that supports consistent, educational guidance.

Can I delete this?
- Optional.
- Keep if your team uses Cursor and wants zero-setup repository-specific guidance.

Use `RESEARCH_SOFTWARE_AI_POLICY.md` as canonical policy.
Use `AGENTS.md` for operational workflow.

- Prefer existing repository tools and workflows.
- Keep edits minimal and aligned with project structure.
- Add tests or validation when behavior changes.
